Cursed enemies have an additional 10% chance to be Stunned
Cursed enemies have 20% reduced Block and Stun Recovery
Cursed enemies have 35% increased Energy Shield recharge delay
Cursed enemies have 50% reduced Energy Shield Recharge rate
Cursed enemies take 25% increased Physical damage
Cursed enemies take 40% increased damage from Damage Over Time effects
items.descrText: Place into an item socket of the right colour to gain this skill. Right click to remove from a socket.

items.secDescrText: Curses all targets in an area, making them less resistant to cold damage and giving them a chance to be frozen by cold damage.
explicitMods: Base duration is 9.90 seconds
Cursed enemies lose 30% Cold Resistance
Cursed enemies have +10% chance to be Frozen by Cold Damage

items.secDescrText: Curses all targets in an area, making them easier for projectiles to pierce and easier to knock back, while reducing their evasion against projectiles.

Projectiles have an additional 40% chance to Pierce Cursed enemies
Hits on Cursed Enemies have an additional 15% chance to Knockback
Cursed enemies have 30% less Evasion against Projectile Attacks
Cursed enemies take 25% increased Damage from Projectiles
